<plot>After a powerful Yakuza mob boss is assassinated in a Tokyo go-go club, his two disgraced body-guards become unrelenting mercenaries who will stop at nothing to reap vengeance-even if it means murdering in the process. Knowing the two vigilantes are on his tail,the Japanese assassin flees to Manhattan to visit with his daughter who attends New York University. But the mercenaries have beaten him to the punch, and are waiting for him when he arrives. What ensues is a widely perverse and deranged game of cat-and-mouse that leads to unspeakable terror...and reveals even more sinister enemies lurking in the shadow of Manhattan</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?245183</url></doc>
